text: Edy Thomi (born 9 June 1929) is a Swiss gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Switzerland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Brig-Glis
